;; Phase 7.4.3 (Doc 31 v2 LOCKED 2026-04-25 §3.3) — Shift-JIS / CP932 /
;; EUC-JP (JIS X 0208 + JIS X 0212) ↔ Unicode mapping tables.
;;
;; *** MVP NOTICE ***
;;
;; This file contains a *partial* (MVP) subset of the full mapping tables
;; (~885 entries instead of ~14000). It validates the codec algorithm in
;; `nelisp-coding.el' against representative Shift-JIS / CP932 / EUC-JP
;; byte sequences. The full ~7000-entry JIS X 0208 + ~845-entry CP932
;; extension + ~6000-entry JIS X 0212 generation is deferred to Phase 7.5
;; via `tools/coding-table-gen.el'.
;;
;; All entries below were generated by `decode-coding-string' under host
;; Emacs `cp932' / `euc-jp' coding systems on 2026-04-25, then frozen here.
;; The same lookup will be re-generated from the canonical Microsoft
;; CP932.TXT + JIS X 0212-1990 sources in Phase 7.5; provenance is recorded
;; in `docs/coding-table-provenance.org'.
;;
;; *** Schema ***
;;
;; Each `defconst' is an alist of `(SOURCE-INT . CODEPOINT)' cons cells:
;; - SOURCE-INT for Shift-JIS / CP932  = (lead << 8) | trail   (16-bit)
;; - SOURCE-INT for EUC-JP X 0208      = (lead << 8) | trail   (16-bit; lead 0xA1-0xFE)
;; - SOURCE-INT for EUC-JP X 0212      = (lead << 8) | trail   (16-bit; the 0x8F
;;                                       prefix is implicit and added by the codec)
;; - CODEPOINT                         = Unicode codepoint (U+0080..U+FFFF for MVP)
;;
;; All tables are sorted by SOURCE-INT ascending; this allows binary search
;; or hash-table promotion in Phase 7.5 if profiling demands.
;;
;; *** Provenance + Golden Hash ***
;;
;; - Source-of-truth: see `docs/coding-table-provenance.org'
;; - Golden SHA-256 hash check: `nelisp-coding-jis-tables-sha256' constant
;;   below; verified by `nelisp-coding-jis-tables-verify-hash' at runtime
;;   per Doc 31 v2 §6.10 + §7.2 (CI で改竄検出).
;;
;; Generator script (Phase 7.5 で real implementation):
;;   `tools/coding-table-gen.el' (skeleton placement、本 MVP では partial
;;    table を hard-coded、real 14000 entry generation は CP932.TXT
;;    download + parse 後置換)。

